<template>
    <MainComponent/>
    <button @click="testdata">CLCK</button>
    {{ test }}
</template>

<script>
    import MainComponent from "../../components/Main/Main.vue";
    import routes from "../../../router"

    export default{
        name: "HomePage",
        components: {
            MainComponent,
        },
        data(){
            test: null
        },
        methods: {
            testdata(){

                const test = routes[0].name

                this.test = test
            }
        }
    }
</script>
